name: Kart Hight Speed 3D
description:
Kart Hight Speed 3D - Gear up for extreme 3D vehicle drive with super speed. Race manager has chosen buggy drivers for this drag race so complete levels in limited time to enjoy speed race in cart.
Game features:
- Awesome cartoon 3D graphics.
- Real race simulator.
- Totally FREE to play.
- For all ages to play.
